cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.DL, cs.CC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with formalizing knowledge bases and queries in terms of a set-theoretic fragment. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper addresses the problem of Conjunctive Query Answering, which is a common problem in AI. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is another likely category as the paper deals with querying knowledge bases. 
- cs.DL (Digital Libraries) is a possible category as the paper deals with description logic, which is used in digital libraries for representing and querying metadata. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possible category as the paper analyzes the computational complexity of the proposed procedures.
